media: v4l: Add new 10-bit packed grayscale format

The new format will be called V4L2_PIX_FMT_Y10P.
It is similar to the V4L2_PIX_FMT_SBGGR10P family formats
but V4L2_PIX_FMT_Y10P is a grayscale format.

